commit.message:
Refactoring+Removal of duplicate checks

Changed the return value of del_groupchat to use
booleans. Removed an extraneous wipe_group_chat and replaced it with a
trim_groupchats function. Eliminated a line of code in tox.c.
Modified del_groupchat to set finished GC's to STATUS_NONE and then
just let all get nailed by reallocation.
Modified reallocate_conferences to crypto_memzero items it takes out.
REMOVED A FUCKING RACE CONDITION LETS GETEM BOIS
